{"tid":1671252,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[國際行動POST] 11月2日 求援國際 堅守自治 維園大集會","createTime":"2019-10-23T11:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T13:43:41.000Z","uid":42194,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"a94949b94b864842f79a3913b7c4863ac7e005b7","tid":1671252,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:05:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">之前問點解係加泰唔係國際？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">而家國際啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AbFbY67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAbFbY67.jpg&h=a763be1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6EwOgTN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6EwOgTN.jpg&h=93f8c39c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cicNxr8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcicNxr8.jpg&h=9a75247a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AyEDD68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAyEDD68.jpg&h=e66a28f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKWOgTO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKWOgTO.jpg&h=2b8b82d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期: 11月2日(六)<br />\n時間：下午三時<br />\n地點: 維多利亞公園中央草坪<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際聚焦，香港集氣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n本港政治問題經過四個多月的發酵蘊釀，已從原本六月頭的本地糾紛，提昇成為國際關注，炙手可熱的重點議題。大家不得不承認，香港正走在近代民主抗爭史的最前線，正在國際眾目睽睽的目光下，撰寫二十一世紀逆權運動史其中一一個最令人深刻的篇章。<br />\n<br />\n民主自由均為現今所有文明社會體系的最低公倍數；大家都深明要一個社會茁壯的成長，民主會是最好的土壤。要一個社會長期健康地屹立不倒，民主將是最好的支柱。相信世界各國目睹香港的民主進程受到窒礙，都能夠伸出援手。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我們決定舉行和平集會，聚集各國打氣聲音和力量，聲援香港，並加強各國對香港現況的了解和關注。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搞手是誰？</span></span><br />\n- 搞手唔係民陣，係民間自發團隊，10月14日香港人權民主法案集氣大會搞手團隊<br />\n- 已經入紙申請緊維園不反對通知書<br />\n- 目標係重演 818 過百萬級數畫面同928-929全球聲援<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">國際求援<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">112</span></span>係國際救援熱線 (source：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/1tTnzqL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1tTnzqL&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=b9db149f\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/1tTnzqL</a>)<br />\n所以11月2日我地將聯同全球各地不同陣線一齊<span style=\"color: gold;\">聲援香港</span><br />\n將會於全球其他不同地點同日有活動聲援香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n包括： <br />\n1. 英國 - 倫敦<br />\n2. 日本 - 東京<br />\n3. 加拿大 - Halifax, Winnipeg<br />\n4. 美國 - DC, LA, San Francisco, Boston<br />\n5. 澳洲 - Sydney, Brisbane, Perth<br />\n(其他各大城市持續聯絡中，期待更多地點加入響應，一齊聲援香港！)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nChannel : <a href=\"https://t.me/HK_112_SOS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHK_112_SOS&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=bd3f219a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HK_112_SOS</a><br />\nGroup : <a href=\"https://t.me/HongKong112\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHongKong112&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=fb9a07ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HongKong112</a> <br />\n<br />\n**已通知警方，待發不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------<br />\n唔好再嘈why Catalonia 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊吹大雞黎個全球大集氣啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊叫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">11月2號維園要人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人！11月2日 維園見！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a86bf1816a4df089171d2e5d5fdf6fa5fb640d33","tid":1671252,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:05:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">11月2號維園要人</span></span>"},{"pid":"070e31c1739a97765a5ecf213ec797a831215fbb","tid":1671252,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:06:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">11月2號維園要人</span></span>"},{"pid":"eb683ea3429fbf81e983cbc3ce4fa682fff422bd","tid":1671252,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:06:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">11月2號維園要人</span></span>"},{"pid":"eba7221c2f75c86937e6f82da9817fde49ffeb64","tid":1671252,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:06:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">11月2號維園要人</span></span>"},{"pid":"1a54e03bafd4f81c5b19643921a8e88940caab97","tid":1671252,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:06:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">11月2號維園要人</span></span>"},{"pid":"0bede31cedfde97e5569301f3775a60fed7b21b8","tid":1671252,"uid":234343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36bbef013b69446